[SN]TITLE[SN]
Why hospitals are under so much pressure

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Hospitals are under more pressure than ever. But why? And why is winter so difficult?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
10 December 2015 Last updated at 06:37 GMT
The ageing population is certainly a factor. But so is the availability of care and support in the community.
Nick Triggle explains the various factors behind the mounting problems the NHS is facing.
